I think try 2 things.

1) You have to return finished effects to the pool explicitly before they can be reused, so you get a slow down because the pool is exhausted and effectively generates -new- ones rather than reuse.
2) You need to remove from ```effects``` as well because otherwise you are iterating over finished effects.


```
    //This is the libGDX array for entry removal speed
    private final Array&lt;PooledEffect&gt; activeEffects = new Array&lt;PooledEffect&gt;(512);
```
